001package com.exoreaction.xorcery.keystores.providers;
002
003import com.exoreaction.xorcery.configuration.Configuration;
004import com.exoreaction.xorcery.secrets.Secrets;
005import com.exoreaction.xorcery.secrets.spi.SecretsProvider;
006import com.exoreaction.xorcery.keystores.KeyStores;
007import jakarta.inject.Inject;
008import org.jvnet.hk2.annotations.ContractsProvided;
009import org.jvnet.hk2.annotations.Service;
010
011import java.io.IOException;
012import java.security.NoSuchAlgorithmException;
013
014@Service(name = "keystore", metadata = "enabled=secrets.keystore.enabled")
015@ContractsProvided(SecretsProvider.class)
016public class KeyStoreSecretsProviderHK2
017        extends KeyStoreSecretsProvider {
018    @Inject
019    public KeyStoreSecretsProviderHK2(Configuration configuration, KeyStores keyStores, Secrets secrets) throws NoSuchAlgorithmException, IOException {
020        super(configuration, keyStores, secrets);
021    }
022}
